text: "Supalonely" is a song by New Zealand singer Benee. It was first released on her 2019 extended play Stella & Steve. It was later released as a single in December of that year. It became very popular on the online video-sharing app TikTok in March 2020. It had about 6.9 billion plays on the app for that month. ==References== Category:2019 songs
title: Supalonely
